rComments: All in all, he's knowledgeable and experienced in the field of IR, but he's very boring. This class has lots of readings, lots of papers and revolves a lot around theories.  He's very helpful and he's a fair grader, but you need to put a lot of effort and work in.
teacherRatingTags: ['Get ready to read', 'So many papers', 'Gives good feedback']

rComments: M. Kaboré, is a very nice person, everything is very clear about what he expects. His midterm and final was very easy! If I can get him next year I diffidently will move my schedule around for him! :)

Decent professor.  Very nice guy both in and outside of class.  Lectures were well organized and clear, but unfortunately quite dull.  He put a lot of effort into the course, but the material was still dry.  Overall he was straightforward and easy to get along with, though.
